Dear Sir,
My friend Mr. V. Tchertkoff has at my request written to you and Mr. Edisson[1] but I feel myself obliged to write to you personally asking you to accept my best thanks for your kindness and to transmit the same to Mr. Edisson for his present. I have received the phonograph and will always using it, remember you and Mr. Edisson.
Yours truly Leo Tolstoy.
14 February 1908.
Милостивый государь!
Искренне ваш Лев Толстой.
